   Electronic Reading Room

      The Electronic Reading Room contains documents specifically identified
      for inclusion by the Freedom of Information Act (FOIA), under 5 U.S.C.
      552 (a)(2)(D). Records created on or after November 1, 1996 are
      available to the public if FTA has determined that they have become, or
      are likely to become the subject of multiple FOIA requests. The number
      of items in the Reading Room will continue to grow.
        * Directives

        * FTA Annual Report for Fiscal Year 1997
        * FTA Federal Register Publications

        2001    2000     1999     1998    1997     1996
        * International Merchant Purchase Authorization Card (IMPAC)

        * One DOT FOIA Page

       Freedom of Information Act Background Information
